Mari menari, mari melayang


1155
01:25:26.538 --> 01:25:29.913
Shamma Si Main Jal Rahi Hoon
Hanya satu malam yang bahagia


1156
01:25:31.372 --> 01:25:34.580
Aao Bujha Do Mujhe
Mari, nyalakan aku


1157
01:25:35.163 --> 01:25:36.455
Kamli...

1158
01:25:41.455 --> 01:25:44.455
Kamli, bangun.

1159
01:25:44.622 --> 01:25:45.747
Bangun.

1160
01:25:47.038 --> 01:25:49.038
Waktunya "bam-bam."

1161
01:25:49.247 --> 01:25:50.622
Bangun. Kau macan.

1162
01:25:50.913 --> 01:25:53.038
Mengaum!

1163
01:25:53.413 --> 01:25:54.372
Bagus. Ayo.

1164
01:26:09.997 --> 01:26:14.538
Na Tu Sharrefon Sa Hai
Kau bukan malaikat


1165
